title: Presidio of San Francisco: Fees & Passes
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Fees & Passes              Fees & Passes       Fees  Park entrance and all National Park Service programs are free of charge at the Presidio.    Passes  National Park passes including the Standard and Military Annual Pass, the Senior Pass and the Access Pass can be obtained at the Presidio Visitor Center, Fort Point Bookstore, and the Warming Hut at the Presidio. Please call the visitor center at 415-561-4323 for hours and availability.
